            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I suspect this is a duplicate of https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/3636\r\n\r\nWe should probably look at the linked PR for that. Unfortunately I don't know coverage very well myself, but I'll try look into it a bit when I have time.\r\n\r\nI suspect it won't make it to the 0.29.x branch though - probably only the 3.0 branch",
